# Standard DB/Web ports (Compose V2)

## Web
- Expose: "${WEB_PORT:-3206}:3206"
- Web app MUST read DB port from env `DB_PORT`; default 3207.

## DB (MySQL)
- Expose: "${DB_HOST_PORT:-3207}:3207"
- Server MUST listen on 3207:
  command:
    - "--port=3207"
    - "--character-set-server=utf8mb4"
    - "--collation-server=utf8mb4_unicode_ci"

## Parity
- Web `DB_PORT` value == DB internal port (3207).
- No `version:` in compose (Compose V2).
